Domestic transactions
	693 - Foreign exchange transferred to another domestic bank
		R - Domestic goods expenditures
		S - Foreign currency insurance, funds, bonds, and investment related expenditures (including accrued interest)
		T - Domestic allowances for family or relatives, donations and inheritance expenditures
		N - Other domestic transaction expenditures
		Z - Source of fund from other overseas transaction receipts (Outward foreign remittances are remitted from other domestic banks, not purchased with TWD)
